ed the adamantium, causing shrapnel to stab into her body.<ref>Wolverine #100</ref>\n\n==Powers and abilities==\nLifeforce was born a mutant with the ability to drain the life force of others, thus revitalizing her own energy or firing the energy from her hands in the form of concussive blasts.\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Lifeforce (comics)}}\n[[Category:Characters created by Jeph Loeb]]\n[[Category:Comics characters introduced in 1994]]\n[[Category:Female supervillains]]\n[[Category:Marvel Comics supervillains]]\n[[Category:Marvel Comics mutants]]\n\n\n{{Marvel-villain-stub}}"}]}}}}